References:
 - https://github.com/lvgl/lv_binding_rust
 - DEP_LV_CONFIG_PATH=`pwd`/examples/include cargo run --example arc --features="alloc,embedded_graphics"

Dependencies:
 - Linux packages: libsdl  (llvm, clang, gcc, ...)
    Fedora: sudo dnf install SDL2-devel
    OpenSuSe: sudo zypper install libsdl2-devel
    Ubuntu: udo apt install libsdl2-dev


Add lvgl to your project
 - cargo add lvgl

Building
  - DEP_LV_CONFIG_PATH=`pwd`/lvgl/config cargo build